13 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP. There is hereby authorized, for the Arkansas
14 House of Representatives for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the following maximum
15 number of part-time or temporary employees, to be known as "Extra Help",
16 payable from funds appropriated herein for such purposes: seven (7) temporary
17 or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to exceed those
18 provided in the Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or its
19 successor, or this act for the appropriate classification.
20
